                        + Bugfix: Content-Type was set to image/jpg instead of
                          image/jpeg.
                        + Bugfix: Some fixes related to PHP4.
                        + Bugfix: Clients with the same username as the admin
                          were able to login to /admin even if the password was
                          different.
